\begin{center}
$-\cotan\left(t_n-\frac{1}{n\pi}\right)=-\cotan(z_n)=n\pi+\frac{\pi}{2}+z_n=n\pi+\frac{\pi}{2}-\frac{1}{n\pi}+o(\frac{1}{n})$.
