$$-\tan\left(t_n-\frac{1}{n\pi}\right)=\frac{1}{n\pi}\left(1+\frac{1}{2n}+o(\frac{1}{n})\right)^{-1}=\frac{1}{n\pi}-\frac{1}{2n^2\pi}+o\left(\frac{1}{n^2}\right),$$
